trans-unit.source: Defines the behavior for an extender control.
trans-unit.target: Definerer virkemåten for en extender-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Extender controls that derive from the <xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl> class require a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control to be on the page.
trans-unit.target: Extender kontroller som avledes fra de <xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>klassen krever en <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontrollen på siden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl> base class performs an explicit test to make sure that a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control exists on the page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>basisklassen utfører en eksplisitt test for å forsikre deg om at en <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontrollen finnes på siden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>

trans-unit.source: However, if you want to create extender controls and the page does not contain an <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control, you can create a class that implements the IExtenderControl interface directly.
trans-unit.target: Men hvis du vil opprette extender kontroller og siden inneholder ikke en <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontrollen, kan du opprette en klasse som implementerer grensesnittet IExtenderControl direkte.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, if you are creating a class that derives from <xref:System.Web.UI.Control> or you are extending an existing control that derives from <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>, you can implement the IExtenderControl interface to support client functionality.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg hvis du oppretter en klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>eller utvider du en eksisterende kontroll som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>, du kan implementere grensesnittet IExtenderControl for å støtte klientfunksjonalitet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control>

trans-unit.source: The IExtenderControl interface registers the script libraries for a control by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptReferences%2A> method, and it registers <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor> objects by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptDescriptors%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IExtenderControl registrerer skriptet biblioteker for en kontroll ved å kalle den <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptReferences%2A>metoden, og registrerer <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor>objekter ved å kalle den <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptDescriptors%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptDescriptors%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor> </xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptReferences%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptDescriptors%2A> method returns an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> list of <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptDescriptors%2A>metoden returnerer en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>liste over <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl.GetScriptDescriptors%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If you extend an existing control type that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> class, implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.IScriptControl> interface.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis du utvider en eksisterende type som er avledet av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>klasse, implementere den <xref:System.Web.UI.IScriptControl>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.IScriptControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>

trans-unit.source: To create an extender control by implementing IExtenderControl, you do the following: - Write code for the control's `OnInit` event to detect and use the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control if it is available on the page.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil opprette en extender-kontroll ved å implementere IExtenderControl, gjør du følgende:-Skriv kode for kontrollens `OnInit` -hendelsen for å oppdage og bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontrollere hvis den er tilgjengelig på siden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: - If the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> is not available on the page, provide alternative means to register required scripts by calling static methods of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> class.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>er ikke tilgjengelig på siden Angi alternativ betyr å registrere nødvendig skript ved å kalle statiske metoder for <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: - Provide protected virtual members for IExtenderControl members.
trans-unit.target: -Angi beskyttede virtuelle medlemmer for IExtenderControl medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: - Provide instance script as a script block that you register with the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control.
trans-unit.target: -Angi forekomsten skript som en skriptblokk du registrere deg i den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: You must do this during the control's `PreRender`, `PreRenderComplete`, or `Render` events.
trans-unit.target: Du må gjøre dette under kontrollens `PreRender`, `PreRenderComplete`, eller `Render` hendelser.

trans-unit.source: - Register the script descriptors during the control's `Render` event.
trans-unit.target: -Registrere skriptet beskrivelser under kontrollens `Render` hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If the page contains an <xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel> control, the page must contain a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis siden inneholder en <xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel>kontroll, siden må inneholde en <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel>

trans-unit.source: You must implement the IExtenderControl interface only when the page does not contain a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Du må implementere grensesnittet IExtenderControl bare når siden ikke inneholder en <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: Registers the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor"></xref> objects for the control and returns an object that contains the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor"></xref> objects for the control.
trans-unit.target: Registrerer den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor"> </xref> objekter for kontrollen, og returnerer et objekt som inneholder den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor"> </xref> objekter for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The server control that the extender is associated with.
trans-unit.target: Serverkontroll extender er knyttet til.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> collection that contains <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>samlingen som inneholder <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptDescriptor"> </xref> objekter.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: Registers the script libraries for the control and returns an enumeration of ECMAScript (JavaScript) files that have been registered as embedded resources.
trans-unit.target: Registrerer skriptet biblioteker for kontrollen, og returnerer en opplisting av ECMAScript (JavaScript)-filer som er registrert som innebygde ressurser.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> collection that contains JavaScript files that have been registered as embedded resources.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>samlingen som inneholder JavaScript-filer som er registrert som innebygde ressurser.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>
